ZH: 我感到疲倦，可能是出了什么病。
EN: I feel exhausted, there might be something wrong with my health.

ZH: 他得了传染病，需要隔离治疗。
EN: He has contracted an infectious disease and needs to be isolated for treatment.

ZH: 她一直饱受着这种难以治愈的疾病。
EN: She has been suffering from this incurable illness.

ZH: 这种疾病的潜伏期很长，不易察觉。
EN: The incubation period of this disease is long and not easily detectable.

ZH: 营养不良可能导致一些疾病的发生。
EN: Malnutrition can lead to the occurrence of certain illnesses.

ZH: 他患有重病，需要接受手术治疗。
EN: He is seriously ill and needs to undergo surgical treatment.

ZH: 这种疾病在冬季更容易传播。
EN: This disease is more easily spread in winter.

ZH: 足够的休息是预防疲劳的最好方法。
EN: Sufficient rest is the best way to prevent fatigue.

ZH: 他的持续疼痛最终被诊断为胃溃疡。
EN: His persistent pain was diagnosed as a stomach ulcer.

ZH: 老年人更容易患上一些慢性疾病。
EN: Older people are more prone to suffer from chronic diseases.

ZH: 预防措施是减少疾病传播的重要手段。
EN: Preventive measures are important means to reduce the spread of diseases.

ZH: 随着年龄增长，患病的风险也在增加。
EN: As age increases, the risk of falling ill also increases.

ZH: 她的递归疲劳会对她的表现产生负面影响。
EN: Her recurrent fatigue will have a negative impact on her performance.

ZH: 聚集性感染病例使得这个城市陷入紧张。
EN: The outbreak of infection cases has put this city on edge.

ZH: 这种罕见疾病的病因尚未完全明确。
EN: The cause of this rare disease has not been fully clarified.

ZH: 预防传染病的最好方式就是勤洗手。
EN: The best way to prevent infectious diseases is to wash hands frequently.

ZH: 他的胃痛可能是由于吃了不新鲜的食物引起的。
EN: His stomach ache may be caused by eating spoiled food.

ZH: 某些疾病需要长期药物治疗才能控制。
EN: Some diseases require long-term medication to be controlled.

ZH: 这种病毒会导致呼吸系统的感染。
EN: This virus can cause respiratory infections.

ZH: 他的年龄很小，容易感染病菌。
EN: Due to his young age, he is easily susceptible to bacterial infection.
